  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/9b33ae5f992cd9c2e1a35985850cb1c6.poster.avif?t=1767539516\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/9b33ae5f992cd9c2e1a35985850cb1c6.mp4?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mimi the Cat – Meow Together</i> is a sokoban-style game that offers the option to play solo or local cooperative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the situation by pushing boxes, stacking them, and even jumping between platforms, acquiring the best strategy to help the adorable kittens reach one of the available beds for a well-deserved rest.<br> <br>In <i>Mimi the Cat – Meow Together</i>, you have two ways to play. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cooperative Mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this mode, you and your friend will take control of different kittens. Teamwork is essential to solve the puzzles, and cooperation is the key here.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/b7f6ad680e225535513f94a226a3215b.poster.avif?t=1767539516\" width=780 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/b7f6ad680e225535513f94a226a3215b.webm?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/b7f6ad680e225535513f94a226a3215b.mp4?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single Player Mode:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In single player mode, the player will need to switch between the available cats, solving the puzzles alone.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/31b623b577c2560c7689a9f9b49b4dff.poster.avif?t=1767539516\" width=780 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/31b623b577c2560c7689a9f9b49b4dff.webm?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/31b623b577c2560c7689a9f9b49b4dff.mp4?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategy and cooperation are crucial for success, but some toys in the environment can help solve the puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/afc998ed3ed8fa7d91f611b4855aedb9.poster.avif?t=1767539516\" width=780 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/afc998ed3ed8fa7d91f611b4855aedb9.webm?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/afc998ed3ed8fa7d91f611b4855aedb9.mp4?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the journey, you'll come across items. Collecting them provides possibilities; customize the kittens, making them even cuter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/e95ee0b3297076fe3966d89ff856322b.poster.avif?t=1767539516\" width=780 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/e95ee0b3297076fe3966d89ff856322b.webm?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/e95ee0b3297076fe3966d89ff856322b.mp4?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no time limit or resources to manage, so you can calmly focus on solving the challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 handcrafted levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local cooperative or single player mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Uniques outfits. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 cute kittens. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/aa4ae1d9773e4c6018dc7da1d5a62702.poster.avif?t=1767539516\" width=780 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/aa4ae1d9773e4c6018dc7da1d5a62702.webm?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509700/extras/aa4ae1d9773e4c6018dc7da1d5a62702.mp4?t=1767539516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack boxes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump between platforms, like a good cat would. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist interface and gameplay. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restart level. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tip on how many boxes are needed. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catchy soundtrack. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun and sweet sokoban with relaxing </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mimi, Branquinho, Nevezinho, Melzinha, Thomas, Nhoque, Pipoca, Cinzendo, Negan, are here to warm your heart ♥.</i></p>",
